Na nri  ndi Moroccan, Ahriche bụ nri agbụrụ Zayanes na Khénifra riri
Aha a sitere na okwu Berber maka osisi; nke a na-ezo aka n'ụzọ nri ahụ si esi nri
Ọ bụ efere nke eriri afọ nke na-ejikarị ganglion, caul, akpa ume ma ọ bụ obi nke ọnyá anụmanụ nwere eriri afọ n'elu osisi oak ma sie ya na coal ọkụ.
